data.description: This 2 bedroom home is conveniently located within North Wilkesboro city limits with close proximity to shopping, dining, the hospital, and downtown activities. This home features fresh paint throughout and a new heat pump (installed this year) with a 10 year transferrable warranty. There is a bonus room that has been used as a bedroom but could be a great dining area or office. The unfinished basement provides plenty of storage. The pull thru driveway can be entered from Hinshaw St or from the alley behind the house. A metal carport and fire pit area are already in place. Schedule your showing today!
